    "The same interaction and action could be performed to reveal the volume at the region set to transparent, as shown in Figure 2F.",
    "In an instant-ngp NeRF model, the volume density grid stores the transparency of the scene learned by the network.",
    "A binary bitfield can be generated based on a transparency threshold and can be used to quickly mask the transparent region from being sampled during raytracing (Müller et al., 2022).",
    "In summary, our system implementation provides many core components for building interactive VR NeRF applications using the Unity game engine to streamline the VR NeRF development process.",
